             was indicted, for that <rs id="t17750426-36-off172" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17750426-36-off172" type="offenceCategory" value="violentTheft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17750426-36-off172" type="offenceSubcategory" value="highwayRobbery"></interp>
               he, in the king's highway, in and upon 
                     <persName id="t17750426-36-victim342" type="victimName">
                        Mary, the <rs id="t17750426-36-viclabel173" type="occupation">wife</rs>
                        <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17750426-36-victim342 t17750426-36-viclabel173"></join> of 
                              
                                 <persName id="t17750426-36-victim344" type="victimName">
